CHAPTER ______
1 AN ACT concerning
2 Public Schools – High School Sports Officiating Services – Procurement
3 Requirements Officials – Payment and Fees
4 FOR the purpose of establishing requirements for local school systems that issue
5 invitations for bids for high school sports officiating services for boys’ and girls’ high
6 school sports; and generally relating to procurement requirements for high school
7 sports officiating services requiring the State Department of Education, in
8 consultation with the Maryland Public Secondary Schools Athletic Association to
9 develop and periodically update a list of similar high school sports that are
10 categorized together; requiring a county board of education to ensure that certain
11 high school sports officials for certain high school sports are provided equal pay;
12 requiring a county board to conduct invitations for bids for high school sports
13 officiating services in a certain manner; and generally relating to compensation for
14 high school sports officials.
15 BY adding to
16 Article – Education
17 Section 4–147
18 Annotated Code of Maryland
19 (2022 Replacement Volume and 2024 Supplement)
