1 (B) A LOCAL SCHOOL SYSTEM SHALL ISSUE INVITATIONS FOR BIDS OR
2 REQUESTS FOR PROPOSALS FOR SIMILAR BOYS’ AND GIRLS’ HIGH SCHOOL SPORTS
3 OFFICIATING SERVICES SIMULTANEOUSLY.
4 (C) (1) A LOCAL SCHOOL SYSTEM MAY ISSUE AN INVITATION FOR BIDS OR
5 A REQUEST FOR PROPOSALS THAT REQUIRES A PROSPECTIVE BIDDER OR OFFEROR
6 TO INCLUDE IN A BID OR AN OFFER BOTH BOYS’ AND GIRLS’ HIGH SCHOOL SPORTS
7 OFFICIATING SERVICES.
8 (2) IF A LOCAL SCHOOL SYSTEM ISSUES SEPARATE INVITATIONS FOR
9 BIDS OR REQUESTS FOR PROPOSALS FOR BOYS’ AND GIRLS’ HIGH SCHOOL SPORTS
10 OFFICIATING SERVICES, THE LOCAL SCHOOL SYSTEM:
11 (I) MAY NOT SET SEPARATE DEADLINES FOR THE SUBMISSION
12 OF BIDS AND OFFERS FOR BOYS’ HIGH SCHOOL SPORTS OFFICIATING SERVICES AND
13 GIRLS’ HIGH SCHOOL SPORTS OFFICIATING SERVICES; AND
14 (II) MAY REQUIRE THAT PROSPECTIVE BIDDERS OR OFFERORS
15 PARTNER TO ENSURE THAT BIDS AND OFFERS FOR BOYS’ HIGH SCHOOL SPORTS
16 OFFICIATING SERVICES ARE ACCOMPANIED BY BIDS AND OFFERS FOR GIRLS’ HIGH
17 SCHOOL SPORTS OFFICIATING SERVICES.
18 (D) A LOCAL SCHOOL SYSTEM SHALL REJECT A BID OR PROPOSAL IF
19 ENTERING INTO A PROCUREMENT CONTRACT BASED ON THE BID OR PROPOSAL
20 WOULD RESULT, FOR SIMILAR BOYS’ AND GIRLS’ HIGH SCHOOL SPORTS, IN THE RATE
21 OF PAY OR ASSIGNING FEES RECEIVED BY INDIVIDUALS OFFICIATING GIRLS’ HIGH
22 SCHOOL SPORTS OR ASSIGNING GIRLS’ HIGH SCHOOL SPORTS OFFICIALS BEING
23 DIFFERENT FROM THE RATE OF PAY OR ASSIGNING FEES FOR INDIVIDUALS
24 OFFICIATING BOYS’ HIGH SCHOOL SPORTS OR ASSIGNING BOYS’ HIGH SCHOOL
25 SPORTS OFFICIALS.
26 (E) THIS SECTION MAY NOT BE CONSTRUED TO PROHIBIT THE PAYMENT OF
27 ASSIGNING FEES AS A BONUS THAT IS PAID OUTSIDE A PROCUREMENT CONTRACT.
28 (F) THE DEPARTMENT MAY DEVELOP GUIDELINES TO ASSIST A LOCAL
29 SCHOOL SYSTEM IN THE IMPLEMENTATION OF THE PROVISIONS OF THIS SECTION,
30 INCLUDING ADDITIONAL CRITERIA FOR DETERMINING WHICH HIGH SCHOOL
31 SPORTS QUALIFY AS SIMILAR BOYS’ AND GIRLS’ HIGH SCHOOL SPORTS.
32 (B) (1) ON OR BEFORE SEPTEMBER 1, 2025, THE DEPARTMENT, IN
33 CONSULTATION WITH THE MARYLAND PUBLIC SECONDARY SCHOOLS ATHLETIC
34 ASSOCIATION SHALL DEVELOP A LIST OF SIMILAR HIGH SCHOOL SPORTS FOR BOYS
35 AND GIRLS.

